            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e9f281a73aec1e86/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e9f281a73aec1e86-f09fcd twpub-e9f281a73aec1e86-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
