            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e9f281a73aec1e86/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e9f281a73aec1e86-f09fcd twpub-e9f281a73aec1e86-6b4cd0\"><p>Please check the Project Gutenberg Web pages for current donation\nmethods and addresses.  Donations are accepted in a number of other\nways including checks, online payments and credit card donations.\nTo donate, please visit: http://pglaf.org/donate</p></div>"
